metadata.name: Kii #1 - 雨月 UGETSU
metadata.description:
This work contains the sounds of rain in Japan that I have recorded. 

As long as you read this text and believe in it, "the sound of rain you hear everywhere" will continue to be "the sound of rain you can only hear in Japan”. 

The view of rain sounds and the moon, which originally cannot coexist, is a symbol of the nonlocality of meme.   


2164x2666 15s MP4   


created by @aldarsign
